<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="9" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="8.[264,1323,283,430]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[312,452,283,309]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Etymology.</emphasis>
This species is named for Rumiñahui, the Inca general who organized resistance against the Spanish in the Quito area after the fall of Atahualpa.
</paragraph>
